Title: Fixed incorrect handling of configurable graph font sizes (since 1.5.0i2)
Level: 1
Component: metrics
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
Version: 1.5.0i3
Date: 1515508805
Class: fix

The font size is configured as PT (points) but was interpreted as PX (pixels)
when rendering in the GUI. This has now been fixed to be interpreted as PT
in all places.
